entries.title_d: The Tusk Cat Run is a series of small smuggling assignments using droid controlled delivery and attack drones.
entries.title: Corellia System: Tusk Cat Run - Leg Two
entries.split_quest_alert: Deliver package three to Tatooine system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the specified location and await the arrival of the delivery drone.
entries.quest_location_d: The next delivery takes place in the Corellia system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Move in close to the delivery drone and use the /dock command to deliver package two and receive package three.
entries.found_loc_d: Navigation waypoint loaded. Meet delivery drone here.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Transfer complete. Package two secure. Package three loaded into your cargo bay. Proceed to Tatooine.
entries.attack_stopped: Tusk Cat Run: < Attack drones destroyed >
entries.attack_notify: Tusk Cat Run: < Attack drones incoming >
